Capítulo 3. Autenticação e autorização

Pagina: 18

Dar permissão de cluster-admin para o usuario jobs
- oc adm policy add-cluster-role-to-user cluster-admin jobs 

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Remover o kubedmin - https://docs.openshift.com/container-platform/4.8/authentication/remove-kubeadmin.html#:~:text=After%20you%20define%20an%20identity,Container%20Platform%20must%20be%20reinstalled.
Exemplo:
- oc delete secrets kubeadmin -n kube-system

